<h2>1. Project Overview</h2>


<div class="card">


<p><b>Project Title:</b> FreshPlate – Smart Indian Meal Planner</p>


<p><b>Website Category:</b> Food & Health / Nutrition Website</p>


<p><b>Problem Statement:</b>

Many students, working professionals, and families find it difficult to maintain healthy Indian eating habits while managing calories, budget, and meal preparation. There is a need for a simple platform that combines meal planning, calorie tracking, grocery management, and Indian recipes.

</p>


<p><b>Why We Chose This Project:</b>

We selected this project because healthy food planning is important in everyday life. Indian cuisine contains many nutritious dishes, but organizing meals daily can be challenging. FreshPlate helps users create healthy meal plans, calculate calories, generate recipes, and manage groceries easily.

</p>


</div>








<h2>2. Project Description</h2>


<p>


FreshPlate – Smart Indian Meal Planner is a responsive web application developed using HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript.

The website helps users maintain a healthy lifestyle by providing Indian diet plans, calorie calculation, budget-friendly meals, grocery management, and recipe generation features.

The main users of this website are students, fitness enthusiasts, working professionals, and families who want convenient meal planning.

The website includes an Indian recipe generator with multiple recipes, calorie calculator, grocery list using Local Storage, water tracking system, animations, and responsive design.

Future improvements include AI-based meal recommendations, user login, nutrition analysis, online recipe API integration, and mobile application development.

</p>








